---
const title = "Baby Knit Sleeping Sack Supplier | China Knit Sack Manufacturer";
const description = "Custom baby knit sleeping sacks from a GOTS certified Chinese factory. Waffle knit, rib knit, organic cotton & bamboo. OEM private label, MOQ 300 pcs.";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description} />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --ink: #1a1a1a;
      --muted: #6b6b6b;
      --line: #e0dbd4;
      --bg: #faf9f7;
      --warm: #f4f1ec;
      --accent: #2d5a3d;
      --accent-light: #e8f0eb;
      --sand: #c9b99a;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.25rem 5vw;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .logo {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--ink);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-cta {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 0.5rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }

    /* HERO — split layout */
    .hero-wrap {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 5rem 5vw 4rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; padding-top: 3rem; }
      .hero-visual { display: none; }
    }
    .breadcrumb {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .breadcrumb a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
    .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .hero-cta:hover { opacity: 0.88; }

    /* VISUAL placeholder — texture block */
    .hero-visual {
      background: var(--warm);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 3px;
      aspect-ratio: 4/5;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .knit-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      gap: 4px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 180px;
    }
    .knit-cell {
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      border-radius: 2px;
      background: var(--sand);
      opacity: 0.4;
    }
    .knit-cell:nth-child(3n) { opacity: 0.7; }
    .knit-cell:nth-child(5n) { opacity: 0.2; }
    .visual-label {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .certs {
      background: var(--warm);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 1.25rem 5vw;
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .cert-tag {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-light);
      padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 5vw; }
    section + section { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
    h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }
    p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* FABRIC CARDS */
    .fabric-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .fabric-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 3px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .fabric-swatch {
      height: 80px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .swatch-waffle { background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, var(--warm) 0px, var(--warm) 6px, #e8e1d6 6px, #e8e1d6 7px), repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--warm) 0px, var(--warm) 6px, #e8e1d6 6px, #e8e1d6 7px); }
    .swatch-rib { background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, var(--warm) 0px, var(--warm) 5px, #ddd5c8 5px, #ddd5c8 7px); }
    .swatch-bamboo { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f0eb 0%, #d4e8d8 50%, #e8f0eb 100%); }
    .swatch-organic { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5efe6 0%, #ede3d5 50%, #f5efe6 100%); }
    .fabric-info { padding: 1.1rem; }
    .fabric-name { font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .fabric-detail { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted); }

    /* SPEC TABLE */
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    th {
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line);
    }
    td {
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    td.muted { color: var(--muted); }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-list { list-style: none; }
    .faq-item {
      padding: 1.25rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .faq-q { font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .faq-a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }

    .cta-block {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 3.5rem 5vw;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-block h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .cta-block p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .cta-email {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .cta-email:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 5vw;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    footer a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="logo">Lianchuang Baby</a>
    <a href="mailto:quaner1234@gmail.com?subject=Baby Knit Sleeping Sack Inquiry" class="nav-cta">Get a Quote</a>
  </nav>

  <div>
    <div class="hero-wrap">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Baby Knit Sleeping Sack
        </div>
        <h1>Baby Knit Sleeping Sack — China Supplier</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Waffle knit, rib knit, bamboo & organic cotton. GOTS certified factory. OEM/ODM, private label, MOQ from 300 pcs.</p>
        <a href="mailto:quaner1234@gmail.com?subject=Baby Knit Sleeping Sack Inquiry" class="hero-cta">Email Us Your Specs →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="knit-grid">
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
          <div class="knit-cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="visual-label">Knit texture illustration</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="certs">
    <span class="cert-tag">GOTS Certified</span>
    <span class="cert-tag">BSCI Audited</span>
    <span class="cert-tag">Waffle Knit</span>
    <span class="cert-tag">Rib Knit</span>
    <span class="cert-tag">MOQ from 300 pcs</span>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2>Knit Fabric Options</h2>
    <div class="fabric-grid">
      <div class="fabric-card">
        <div class="fabric-swatch swatch-waffle"></div>
        <div class="fabric-info">
          <div class="fabric-name">Classic Square Waffle</div>
          <div class="fabric-detail">Textured grid construction. Breathable, good stretch recovery. Popular for 1.0–2.5 TOG.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fabric-card">
        <div class="fabric-swatch swatch-rib"></div>
        <div class="fabric-info">
          <div class="fabric-name">Vertical Rib Knit</div>
          <div class="fabric-detail">Clean vertical texture, excellent drape. Often used for 0.5–1.0 TOG summer sacks.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fabric-card">
        <div class="fabric-swatch swatch-bamboo"></div>
        <div class="fabric-info">
          <div class="fabric-name">Bamboo Knit</div>
          <div class="fabric-detail">Ultra-soft, thermoregulating. Ideal for sensitive skin. GOTS-certified available.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fabric-card">
        <div class="fabric-swatch swatch-organic"></div>
        <div class="fabric-info">
          <div class="fabric-name">Organic Cotton Knit</div>
          <div class="fabric-detail">GOTS certified. Durable, easy-care, works for 1.0–3.5 TOG with appropriate filling.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Standard Specifications</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Spec</th>
          <th>Options / Range</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>TOG Rating</td>
          <td class="muted">0.5 / 1.0 / 2.5 (custom available)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Sizes</td>
          <td class="muted">0–6M / 6–18M / 18–36M (custom sizing available)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Fabric Weight</td>
          <td class="muted">180–280 gsm depending on construction and TOG</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Closure</td>
          <td class="muted">2-way zip, shoulder snap, or combination</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Arm opening</td>
          <td class="muted">Sleeveless standard; with sleeves available</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>MOQ</td>
          <td class="muted">300 pcs per colorway / style</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Sample lead time</td>
          <td class="muted">15–20 days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Bulk lead time</td>
          <td class="muted">45–60 days after sample approval</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Certifications</td>
          <td class="muted">GOTS (organic), BSCI (social compliance)</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <ul class="faq-list">
      <li class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">What is a knit sleeping sack vs. a woven sleeping bag?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Knit fabric has natural stretch, giving the sack a soft, body-conforming fit. Woven sleeping bags use tighter non-stretch fabric, which is more structured. Knit sacks are increasingly preferred for loungewear-style aesthetics and comfort.</div>
      </li>
      <li class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">Can I get GOTS certification documentation?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. Our factory holds GOTS certification. Transaction certificates and scope certificates are available upon request.</div>
      </li>
      <li class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">Can you match a Pantone color for the knit?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes, we can dye to a target Pantone reference. A lab dip will be sent for your approval before bulk production.</div>
      </li>
      <li class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">Do you offer different TOG ratings in the same style?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. The same knit sack design can be produced in multiple TOG ratings by adjusting the filling weight. MOQ applies per TOG variant.</div>
      </li>
      <li class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-q">What's the minimum order quantity?</div>
        <div class="faq-a">300 pieces per colorway/style. For mixed colors of the same style, please enquire for combined MOQ options.</div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-block">
    <h2>Source Baby Knit Sleeping Sacks Direct from Factory</h2>
    <p>Share your design reference, fabric choice, TOG, and quantity. We'll respond within 24 hours.</p>
    <a href="mailto:quaner1234@gmail.com?subject=Baby Knit Sleeping Sack Inquiry" class="cta-email">
      quaner1234@gmail.com
    </a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Taian Lianchuang Textile Co., Ltd. &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="/">lianchuangbaby.com</a></p>
